1
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:32,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好漂亮呀！</font></font></font>

2
00:03:27,792 --> 00:03:28,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">各位客官</font></font></font>

3
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:31,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">担搁大家一会，很快就点着了</font></font></font>

4
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不好意思，对不起呀！</font></font></font>

5
00:03:45,333 --> 00:03:48,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">老伯，你这样点灯是点不着的</font></font></font>

6
00:03:48,375 --> 00:03:50,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你只有油，没有灯芯</font></font></font>

7
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:51,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道</font></font></font>

8
00:03:53,042 --> 00:03:56,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是灯芯不见了，有什么办法呢？</font></font></font>

9
00:03:56,792 --> 00:03:57,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">买一根喏</font></font></font>

10
00:04:01,333 --> 00:04:02,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有道理…</font></font></font>

11
00:04:02,792 --> 00:04:05,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">姑娘，请问你</font></font></font>

12
00:04:05,875 --> 00:04:09,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果如来佛祖那盏神灯的灯芯不见了</font></font></font>

13
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上哪去买？</font></font></font>

14
00:04:11,083 --> 00:04:12,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早知道你有问题，现身吧！</font></font></font>

15
00:04:19,417 --> 00:04:22,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来是二郎神和南天门的四大天王</font></font></font>

16
00:04:22,917 --> 00:04:25,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞，你跟你姐姐青霞仙子</font></font></font>

17
00:04:25,542 --> 00:04:26,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来是佛祖日月明灯里面</font></font></font>

18
00:04:27,042 --> 00:04:28,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">缠在一起的灯芯</font></font></font>

19
00:04:28,292 --> 00:04:29,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你竟然擅自离开天庭</font></font></font>

20
00:04:29,792 --> 00:04:30,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还到处跟人说</font></font></font>

21
00:04:30,875 --> 00:04:33,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁能拔出你手中的紫青宝剑</font></font></font>

22
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:34,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是你的如意郎君</font></font></font>

23
00:04:35,167 --> 00:04:36,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你是神仙怎么能动凡心</font></font></font>

24
00:04:36,875 --> 00:04:38,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">假如邪魔外道把你的宝剑拔出来</font></font></font>

25
00:04:38,792 --> 00:04:40,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们仙界岂不是成为笑柄</font></font></font>

26
00:04:41,042 --> 00:04:42,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神仙也好，妖怪也好</font></font></font>

27
00:04:43,042 --> 00:04:45,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">剑只有我跟我的意中人能拔得出</font></font></font>

28
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:46,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算他是妖怪</font></font></font>

29
00:04:46,542 --> 00:04:48,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也会一生一世跟着他</font></font></font>

30
00:04:48,417 --> 00:04:51,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果不能跟我喜欢的人在一起的话</font></font></font>

31
00:04:51,792 --> 00:04:54,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算让我做玉皇大帝我也不会开心</font></font></font>

32
00:04:54,667 --> 00:04:56,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一派胡言</font></font></font>

33
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:57,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">既然你执迷不悟</font></font></font>

34
00:04:57,458 --> 00:04:58,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我今天就要替天行道</font></font></font>

35
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:00,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要你在人间仙界消失</font></font></font>

36
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:02,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只羡鸳鸯不羡仙，消失就消失</font></font></font>

37
00:05:03,542 --> 00:05:04,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放肆！</font></font></font>

38
00:06:18,042 --> 00:06:19,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用说！</font></font></font>

39
00:06:19,167 --> 00:06:21,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这件事谁说出去，我就杀了他！</font></font></font>

40
00:06:22,958 --> 00:06:24,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我说了不用再说了</font></font></font>

41
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:25,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是啊！</font></font></font>

42
00:06:25,333 --> 00:06:27,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的吼天犬在那边骑着一条母狗</font></font></font>

43
00:06:27,875 --> 00:06:28,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">连牠都动了凡心</font></font></font>

44
00:06:29,792 --> 00:06:30,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天晚上我就杀了牠大家一块吃</font></font></font>

45
00:06:30,917 --> 00:06:31,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好啊…</font></font></font>

46
00:06:31,833 --> 00:06:33,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们早就这么想了</font></font></font>

47
00:06:47,375 --> 00:06:48,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶</font></font></font>

48
00:07:11,708 --> 00:07:12,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶</font></font></font>

49
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:15,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎会这样的，人呢？</font></font></font>

50
00:07:45,708 --> 00:07:46,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神仙？</font></font></font>

51
00:07:48,833 --> 00:07:49,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妖怪</font></font></font>

52
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谢谢</font></font></font>

53
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:57,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞不要乱闯</font></font></font>

54
00:07:58,875 --> 00:08:00,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞？</font></font></font>

55
00:08:00,917 --> 00:08:03,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为我看不懂啊？水帘洞嘛！</font></font></font>

56
00:08:10,208 --> 00:08:13,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞，这个名字蛮好听的</font></font></font>

57
00:08:17,292 --> 00:08:19,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就叫你盘丝洞吧</font></font></font>

58
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:23,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好，我以后就住在这儿</font></font></font>

59
00:08:24,542 --> 00:08:25,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">慢着</font></font></font>

60
00:08:35,292 --> 00:08:36,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我现在郑重宣布</font></font></font>

61
00:08:36,792 --> 00:08:38,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个山头所有东西都属于我的</font></font></font>

62
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:39,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">包括你在内</font></font></font>

63
00:08:40,208 --> 00:08:41,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我？</font></font></font>

64
00:08:41,583 --> 00:08:42,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是呀！</font></font></font>

65
00:08:42,583 --> 00:08:44,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就像我的骡子一样，给你盖个章</font></font></font>

66
00:08:50,875 --> 00:08:51,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在是我的人了</font></font></font>

67
00:08:52,417 --> 00:08:54,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果有人欺负你呢，就报我的名字</font></font></font>

68
00:08:54,792 --> 00:08:57,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">从今天起，我叫盘丝大仙</font></font></font>

69
00:08:58,958 --> 00:09:00,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝大仙？</font></font></font>

70
00:09:01,292 --> 00:09:02,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年前？</font></font></font>

71
00:09:09,542 --> 00:09:11,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你没有变成孙悟空托世</font></font></font>

72
00:09:11,625 --> 00:09:14,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是因为你还没遇见给你三颗痣的人</font></font></font>

73
00:09:32,125 --> 00:09:33,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芝麻开门</font></font></font>

74
00:09:35,542 --> 00:09:36,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芝麻关门</font></font></font>

75
00:09:50,125 --> 00:09:51,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不信…</font></font></font>

76
00:09:51,875 --> 00:09:52,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不要当猴子</font></font></font>

77
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要去救晶晶</font></font></font>

78
00:09:56,083 --> 00:09:57,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">拜托你把宝盒还给我</font></font></font>

79
00:09:58,583 --> 00:10:00,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芝麻开门</font></font></font>

80
00:10:10,208 --> 00:10:12,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没道理啊，明明听到她说芝麻开门的</font></font></font>

81
00:10:31,875 --> 00:10:32,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芝麻开门</font></font></font>

82
00:10:38,458 --> 00:10:39,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你赖皮</font></font></font>

83
00:10:45,958 --> 00:10:48,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怕了你了，想别的办法</font></font></font>

84
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上山！</font></font></font>

85
00:10:55,542 --> 00:10:56,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这一边</font></font></font>

86
00:10:56,583 --> 00:10:58,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">芝麻开门</font></font></font>

87
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:01,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁啊？</font></font></font>

88
00:11:06,667 --> 00:11:08,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么压得四分五裂了？</font></font></font>

89
00:11:20,875 --> 00:11:24,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！好棒呀！</font></font></font>

90
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有了这个月光宝盒</font></font></font>

91
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:32,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以后就不怕被青霞姐姐追杀</font></font></font>

92
00:11:34,333 --> 00:11:37,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出来吧！鬼鬼崇崇的，害羞呀你？</font></font></font>

93
00:11:41,167 --> 00:11:43,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个月光宝盒呢…　﹣我的！</font></font></font>

94
00:11:44,667 --> 00:11:47,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我说过了，这里所有东西都是我的</font></font></font>

95
00:11:47,375 --> 00:11:48,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想干嘛？</font></font></font>

96
00:11:48,125 --> 00:11:48,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没…</font></font></font>

97
00:11:49,417 --> 00:11:50,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我听说你要走</font></font></font>

98
00:11:50,917 --> 00:11:51,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">能不能带我一起走呀？</font></font></font>

99
00:11:52,583 --> 00:11:53,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你也被人追杀呀？</font></font></font>

100
00:11:53,708 --> 00:11:55,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我赶着去救人</font></font></font>

101
00:11:55,417 --> 00:11:56,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救谁啊？</font></font></font>

102
00:11:56,333 --> 00:11:57,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救我娘子</font></font></font>

103
00:11:57,708 --> 00:12:00,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是白晶晶嘛，你认识她的</font></font></font>

104
00:12:00,292 --> 00:12:01,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不认识</font></font></font>

105
00:12:01,167 --> 00:12:02,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道，不过你很快就会认识她了</font></font></font>

106
00:12:02,792 --> 00:12:04,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为她将会做你的徒弟</font></font></font>

107
00:12:04,417 --> 00:12:06,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还有这个宝盒呢…</font></font></font>

108
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的！</font></font></font>

109
00:12:07,125 --> 00:12:07,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道</font></font></font>

110
00:12:07,958 --> 00:12:09,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过其实呢，是我给你</font></font></font>

111
00:12:09,292 --> 00:12:11,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">然后你再…在那个时候交给我</font></font></font>

112
00:12:11,292 --> 00:12:13,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么才会有我回到这里来</font></font></font>

113
00:12:13,333 --> 00:12:14,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">然后又交还给你</font></font></font>

114
00:12:14,583 --> 00:12:15,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你明白吗？</font></font></font>

115
00:12:16,042 --> 00:12:20,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我明白？你神经病</font></font></font>

116
00:12:22,667 --> 00:12:23,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">反正你一定要带我走就对</font></font></font>

117
00:12:23,917 --> 00:12:25,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我为什么要对你这么好？</font></font></font>

118
00:12:25,708 --> 00:12:26,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为你是我的主人</font></font></font>

119
00:12:26,708 --> 00:12:28,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你走了我一个人留在这里什么意思</font></font></font>

120
00:12:28,917 --> 00:12:29,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的吗？</font></font></font>

121
00:12:30,542 --> 00:12:31,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">坐</font></font></font>

122
00:12:32,417 --> 00:12:33,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">地下</font></font></font>

123
00:12:35,292 --> 00:12:36,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">手</font></font></font>

124
00:12:38,625 --> 00:12:41,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乖啊！待会给你买件新衣服</font></font></font>

125
00:12:41,458 --> 00:12:43,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">让你回去见你娘子啊</font></font></font>

126
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:45,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叫啊！</font></font></font>

127
00:12:45,083 --> 00:12:45,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喔</font></font></font>

128
00:12:45,625 --> 00:12:46,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">用心点</font></font></font>

129
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:49,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喔…</font></font></font>

130
00:12:56,875 --> 00:12:58,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">仙子…</font></font></font>

131
00:12:59,667 --> 00:13:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快点呀，月亮出来了</font></font></font>

132
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走啦</font></font></font>

133
00:13:02,792 --> 00:13:03,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去哪儿？</font></font></font>

134
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:05,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不走啊？</font></font></font>

135
00:13:05,375 --> 00:13:07,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不走把宝盒给我，我走啊</font></font></font>

136
00:13:07,292 --> 00:13:08,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么宝盒？</font></font></font>

137
00:13:09,833 --> 00:13:12,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是不会再等到明天晚上了</font></font></font>

138
00:13:12,333 --> 00:13:13,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我告诉你</font></font></font>

139
00:13:13,583 --> 00:13:14,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你快点啦，还说</font></font></font>

140
00:13:14,583 --> 00:13:15,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等一下你那个贱人姐姐又出来害你了</font></font></font>

141
00:13:16,583 --> 00:13:19,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贱人，到处跟人家说我害她</font></font></font>

142
00:13:20,208 --> 00:13:20,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？</font></font></font>

143
00:13:21,917 --> 00:13:23,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就是那个贱人的姐姐</font></font></font>

144
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要听她胡说八道</font></font></font>

145
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:26,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">至尊宝</font></font></font>

146
00:13:28,667 --> 00:13:29,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">至尊宝</font></font></font>

147
00:13:31,708 --> 00:13:33,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你昨晚怎么不叫醒我呀？</font></font></font>

148
00:13:36,458 --> 00:13:37,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么了？</font></font></font>

149
00:13:40,333 --> 00:13:42,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你到那儿去？站住</font></font></font>

150
00:13:44,042 --> 00:13:44,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">坐下</font></font></font>

151
00:13:48,042 --> 00:13:48,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">椅子</font></font></font>

152
00:13:57,542 --> 00:13:58,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么了？</font></font></font>

153
00:14:00,667 --> 00:14:01,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么这样看我？</font></font></font>

154
00:14:03,417 --> 00:14:04,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看到什么啦？</font></font></font>

155
00:14:06,083 --> 00:14:07,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看到她啦？</font></font></font>

156
00:14:07,667 --> 00:14:09,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你真的看到我姐姐吗？</font></font></font>

157
00:14:09,542 --> 00:14:10,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她那么快就来啦</font></font></font>

158
00:14:11,333 --> 00:14:12,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她跟你说了什么？</font></font></font>

159
00:14:13,792 --> 00:14:15,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要相信她，她是神经病</font></font></font>

160
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:19,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可能她前世跟我斗得太厉害</font></font></font>

161
00:14:20,042 --> 00:14:21,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以后来佛祖</font></font></font>

162
00:14:21,125 --> 00:14:23,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把我们两个卷在一起变成一根灯芯</font></font></font>

163
00:14:23,292 --> 00:14:24,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要我们苦练修行</font></font></font>

164
00:14:24,875 --> 00:14:26,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">化解这段恩怨</font></font></font>

165
00:14:27,292 --> 00:14:29,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可惜事与愿违</font></font></font>

166
00:14:29,458 --> 00:14:30,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在斗得比以前更厉害</font></font></font>

167
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要说那么多了</font></font></font>

168
00:14:32,625 --> 00:14:33,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们快走吧！</font></font></font>

169
00:14:37,875 --> 00:14:39,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为我精神分裂啦</font></font></font>

170
00:14:42,208 --> 00:14:45,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我没有，那个真的是我姐姐</font></font></font>

171
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:47,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不相信是吗？</font></font></font>

172
00:14:48,542 --> 00:14:50,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来呀，拿来呀</font></font></font>

173
00:14:51,125 --> 00:14:52,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们把手绑在一起</font></font></font>

174
00:14:52,958 --> 00:14:53,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天晚上就知道</font></font></font>

175
00:15:07,417 --> 00:15:08,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我看今晚不会有月光了</font></font></font>

176
00:15:09,833 --> 00:15:10,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？</font></font></font>

177
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:14,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贱人</font></font></font>

178
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你跑不出我的五指山</font></font></font>

179
00:15:25,583 --> 00:15:26,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贵姓啊？</font></font></font>

180
00:15:26,625 --> 00:15:27,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">姓林！</font></font></font>

181
00:15:29,125 --> 00:15:32,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来你就是我大哥说的那个林青霞</font></font></font>

182
00:15:32,125 --> 00:15:33,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你大哥？</font></font></font>

183
00:15:33,667 --> 00:15:36,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">昨天被你打那个家伙，叫做至尊宝</font></font></font>

184
00:15:36,458 --> 00:15:37,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你呢？</font></font></font>

185
00:15:38,792 --> 00:15:40,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是他的双胞胎弟弟叫至尊玉</font></font></font>

186
00:15:41,417 --> 00:15:43,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">至尊宝？玉尊玉？想骗我啊？</font></font></font>

187
00:15:45,583 --> 00:15:46,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你真是聪明伶俐</font></font></font>

188
00:15:46,958 --> 00:15:48,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">其实我大哥的真名叫秦汉</font></font></font>

189
00:15:49,042 --> 00:15:50,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我叫秦祥林</font></font></font>

190
00:15:50,208 --> 00:15:51,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你在这里干什么？</font></font></font>

191
00:15:51,958 --> 00:15:53,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我很仰慕你</font></font></font>

192
00:15:53,958 --> 00:15:54,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你仰慕我？</font></font></font>

193
00:15:55,333 --> 00:15:58,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">岂止仰慕，简直害怕失去你</font></font></font>

194
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以跟你绑在一起</font></font></font>

195
00:16:00,875 --> 00:16:02,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你接受我对你的爱吧</font></font></font>

196
00:16:02,458 --> 00:16:03,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们一起远走高飞</font></font></font>

197
00:16:04,583 --> 00:16:06,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">爱我就要付出代价</font></font></font>

198
00:16:08,125 --> 00:16:10,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别说了，可能你姐姐恨你入骨</font></font></font>

199
00:16:10,958 --> 00:16:12,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我今天晚上骗她我杀了你</font></font></font>

200
00:16:12,250 --> 00:16:13,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以后就可安心</font></font></font>

201
00:16:13,833 --> 00:16:15,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以我要你身上一件信物给她看</font></font></font>

202
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你有什么颈炼…</font></font></font>

203
00:16:17,542 --> 00:16:20,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">手饰，珠宝，月光宝盒什么…</font></font></font>

204
00:16:21,333 --> 00:16:23,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好呀，不过那些没有用</font></font></font>

205
00:16:23,333 --> 00:16:25,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你今天晚上拿我的紫青宝剑给她看</font></font></font>

206
00:16:25,167 --> 00:16:26,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她一定会相信的</font></font></font>

207
00:16:28,458 --> 00:16:29,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也好</font></font></font>

208
00:16:40,958 --> 00:16:42,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">居然是他</font></font></font>

209
00:16:46,792 --> 00:16:49,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">趁现在天没黑，带我到市集去走走吧</font></font></font>

210
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:00,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么了？</font></font></font>

211
00:17:01,375 --> 00:17:02,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干什么？</font></font></font>

212
00:17:02,375 --> 00:17:03,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的心跳得好厉害</font></font></font>

213
00:17:04,542 --> 00:17:05,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那怎么办？</font></font></font>

214
00:17:05,708 --> 00:17:06,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来</font></font></font>

215
00:17:07,417 --> 00:17:08,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在大师兄变了人样</font></font></font>

216
00:17:08,917 --> 00:17:10,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还跟紫霞仙子在一起</font></font></font>

217
00:17:10,875 --> 00:17:12,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道抓师父这件事</font></font></font>

218
00:17:12,583 --> 00:17:14,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞仙子也有份？</font></font></font>

219
00:17:14,208 --> 00:17:15,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们跟紧他不要打草惊蛇</font></font></font>

220
00:17:15,958 --> 00:17:17,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">论智慧跟武功</font></font></font>

221
00:17:17,708 --> 00:17:19,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一直比他高一点点</font></font></font>

222
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:21,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是现在多了一个紫霞仙子</font></font></font>

223
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:23,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她恐怕比我高一点点了</font></font></font>

224
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:24,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这边有我嘛</font></font></font>

225
00:17:24,667 --> 00:17:26,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是因为多了你这个累赘</font></font></font>

226
00:17:26,292 --> 00:17:27,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他才会高我一点点</font></font></font>

227
00:17:27,708 --> 00:17:29,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个猪头切一半给我，谢谢</font></font></font>

228
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">猪头不卖，猪鞭要不要？</font></font></font>

229
00:17:40,125 --> 00:17:41,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干什么？</font></font></font>

230
00:17:41,125 --> 00:17:42,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的意中人在附近</font></font></font>

231
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看到他了？</font></font></font>

232
00:17:43,792 --> 00:17:44,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有</font></font></font>

233
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为我的紫青宝剑发出嘟嘟的讯号</font></font></font>

234
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:48,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哪来的嘟嘟声</font></font></font>

235
00:17:49,458 --> 00:17:52,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">嘟…嘟…嘟…对不对呀？</font></font></font>

236
00:17:52,833 --> 00:17:54,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你嘟的，宝剑没有嘟呀</font></font></font>

237
00:17:54,625 --> 00:17:57,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道你听不见才嘟给你听</font></font></font>

238
00:17:58,083 --> 00:18:00,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">完了我好害怕啊！</font></font></font>

239
00:18:00,708 --> 00:18:02,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不骗你，我真的好害怕啊！</font></font></font>

240
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:03,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怕什么？</font></font></font>

241
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这段姻缘是上天安排的你说我怕不怕</font></font></font>

242
00:18:07,583 --> 00:18:08,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">又来了？</font></font></font>

243
00:18:08,625 --> 00:18:10,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊！我的心在跳</font></font></font>

244
00:18:11,375 --> 00:18:12,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的宝剑在嘟</font></font></font>

245
00:18:13,042 --> 00:18:13,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么办？</font></font></font>

246
00:18:14,042 --> 00:18:15,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我怎么跟他说，怎么跟他说呢？</font></font></font>

247
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就告诉他说</font></font></font>

248
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:18,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这是上天安排了这么一段姻缘</font></font></font>

249
00:18:20,125 --> 00:18:21,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他不喜欢我，怎么办？</font></font></font>

250
00:18:22,417 --> 00:18:23,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他有老婆怎么办呀？</font></font></font>

251
00:18:23,875 --> 00:18:26,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你管他那么多，上天的安排是最大</font></font></font>

252
00:18:28,417 --> 00:18:29,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的？</font></font></font>

253
00:18:29,292 --> 00:18:32,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上天安排的，还不够你臭屁的啊？</font></font></font>

254
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:34,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊！对…</font></font></font>

255
00:18:40,875 --> 00:18:41,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他来了</font></font></font>

256
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不会是我吧？</font></font></font>

257
00:18:44,792 --> 00:18:47,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎…就是你，你怎么知道？就是你</font></font></font>

258
00:18:47,583 --> 00:18:48,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道我刚才都不知</font></font></font>

259
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么跟你说才好</font></font></font>

260
00:18:50,917 --> 00:18:51,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你真是聪明啊</font></font></font>

261
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:53,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是我有老婆了</font></font></font>

262
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:57,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道，可是我也没办法呀</font></font></font>

263
00:18:58,375 --> 00:19:00,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这段姻缘是上天安排的最大嘛</font></font></font>

264
00:19:01,375 --> 00:19:03,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喏！你现在呢只要甩掉你哪个老婆</font></font></font>

265
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">然后跟我一起走</font></font></font>

266
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也好啊！</font></font></font>

267
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:09,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好啊？</font></font></font>

268
00:19:10,292 --> 00:19:11,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是很好呀！</font></font></font>

269
00:19:12,125 --> 00:19:14,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么我们大家立刻开始这段感情吧！</font></font></font>

270
00:19:14,542 --> 00:19:16,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！就立刻开始！</font></font></font>

271
00:19:16,208 --> 00:19:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你先亲我一下吧</font></font></font>

272
00:19:17,708 --> 00:19:19,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也好，自动送上门来</font></font></font>

273
00:19:19,417 --> 00:19:20,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来啊！</font></font></font>

274
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来，拿出来</font></font></font>

275
00:19:35,083 --> 00:19:35,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你骗我</font></font></font>

276
00:19:36,417 --> 00:19:37,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你根本不想亲我</font></font></font>

277
00:19:37,833 --> 00:19:39,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你刚刚说的话全都是骗我的</font></font></font>

278
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:42,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是认真的，你先把宝盒拿出来</font></font></font>

279
00:19:43,542 --> 00:19:45,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要不要我把心托出来给你看看？</font></font></font>

280
00:19:45,625 --> 00:19:46,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用，我自己来</font></font></font>

281
00:19:55,667 --> 00:19:58,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的心怎么像椰子一样</font></font></font>

282
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小姐，不可否认我长得很丑</font></font></font>

283
00:20:01,083 --> 00:20:05,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是我很温柔，而且永远不会说谎</font></font></font>

284
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:06,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你老实告诉我</font></font></font>

285
00:20:07,583 --> 00:20:09,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他跟他娘子是不是很恩爱</font></font></font>

286
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁敢惹我就杀谁</font></font></font>

287
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:15,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提大哥你看看</font></font></font>

288
00:20:16,792 --> 00:20:18,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看看！</font></font></font>

289
00:20:21,625 --> 00:20:22,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的不动啦</font></font></font>

290
00:20:27,083 --> 00:20:28,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我懂了</font></font></font>

291
00:20:30,833 --> 00:20:31,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">搜搜看</font></font></font>

292
00:20:38,083 --> 00:20:40,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">老兄，这是什么意思啊？</font></font></font>

293
00:20:40,667 --> 00:20:42,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我看你身裁好，所以摸摸看了</font></font></font>

294
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:45,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是这样的，那就请继续摸啦</font></font></font>

295
00:20:45,208 --> 00:20:47,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没事了，继续摸</font></font></font>

296
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁的手啊？</font></font></font>

297
00:20:49,958 --> 00:20:50,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

298
00:20:51,958 --> 00:20:53,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">拿开！</font></font></font>

299
00:20:53,875 --> 00:20:55,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妖怪呀</font></font></font>

300
00:20:58,292 --> 00:20:59,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">闹够了没有？</font></font></font>

301
00:21:12,833 --> 00:21:14,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你别生气，我是跟你闹着玩的</font></font></font>

302
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好好照顾姐姐</font></font></font>

303
00:21:17,292 --> 00:21:18,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她一定会给你的</font></font></font>

304
00:21:18,667 --> 00:21:19,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我怎么敢生你的气呢，大姐</font></font></font>

305
00:21:19,917 --> 00:21:22,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把你当观世音供奉着还来不及呢</font></font></font>

306
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:32,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天黑了，我要去找姐姐了</font></font></font>

307
00:21:32,917 --> 00:21:33,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祝你好运</font></font></font>

308
00:21:38,625 --> 00:21:40,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有好运才怪</font></font></font>

309
00:21:47,958 --> 00:21:49,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">青霞</font></font></font>

310
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你在那里呀？</font></font></font>

311
00:21:51,792 --> 00:21:53,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出来呀</font></font></font>

312
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我已经杀了你妹妹啦</font></font></font>

313
00:22:09,708 --> 00:22:11,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空你这个畜生</font></font></font>

314
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:13,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你为了跟牛魔王的妹妹成亲</font></font></font>

315
00:22:13,708 --> 00:22:16,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">居然把你师父唐三藏作贺礼</font></font></font>

316
00:22:16,417 --> 00:22:19,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还约了妖魔鬼怪一起吃唐僧肉</font></font></font>

317
00:22:21,208 --> 00:22:22,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">三八婆！</font></font></font>

318
00:22:23,833 --> 00:22:25,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你追了我三天三夜</font></font></font>

319
00:22:25,792 --> 00:22:27,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为你是女人，我才不杀你</font></font></font>

320
00:22:28,083 --> 00:22:29,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别要以为我是怕了你</font></font></font>

321
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:32,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空</font></font></font>

322
00:22:33,042 --> 00:22:36,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么可以这样跟观音姐姐讲话呢</font></font></font>

323
00:22:37,583 --> 00:22:38,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">闭嘴！</font></font></font>

324
00:22:39,292 --> 00:22:40,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又吓我！</font></font></font>

325
00:22:41,875 --> 00:22:43,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空，唐三藏？</font></font></font>

326
00:22:44,125 --> 00:22:46,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道你已经犯了弥天大罪了？</font></font></font>

327
00:22:47,333 --> 00:22:50,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还抢了紫霞仙子的月光宝盒</font></font></font>

328
00:22:50,167 --> 00:22:52,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">分明就是想避开我</font></font></font>

329
00:22:53,542 --> 00:22:54,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">既然避不了</font></font></font>

330
00:22:54,708 --> 00:22:56,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我老孙就跟你决一死战啦</font></font></font>

331
00:22:58,500 --> 00:22:59,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干什么呀？</font></font></font>

332
00:23:11,375 --> 00:23:13,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，你也真调皮啊</font></font></font>

333
00:23:13,625 --> 00:23:16,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我教你不要乱扔东西啊</font></font></font>

334
00:23:16,125 --> 00:23:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乱扔东西是不对的</font></font></font>

335
00:23:18,083 --> 00:23:20,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我话没说完，你怎把棍子也给扔掉了</font></font></font>

336
00:23:20,292 --> 00:23:21,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒是宝物</font></font></font>

337
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:24,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乱扔会染污环境！</font></font></font>

338
00:23:26,042 --> 00:23:27,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">砸着小朋友怎么办？</font></font></font>

339
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:28,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算砸不着小朋友</font></font></font>

340
00:23:28,958 --> 00:23:31,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">砸着花花草草也不好嘛</font></font></font>

341
00:23:33,667 --> 00:23:34,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干什么？</font></font></font>

342
00:23:35,125 --> 00:23:36,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放手！</font></font></font>

343
00:23:36,458 --> 00:23:37,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想要呀？</font></font></font>

344
00:23:37,500 --> 00:23:39,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想要说清楚就行了嘛</font></font></font>

345
00:23:39,167 --> 00:23:40,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想要的话我会给你的</font></font></font>

346
00:23:40,417 --> 00:23:42,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想要我当然不会不给你的</font></font></font>

347
00:23:42,542 --> 00:23:44,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不可能你说要我不给你的</font></font></font>

348
00:23:44,542 --> 00:23:46,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说不要我却偏要给你</font></font></font>

349
00:23:46,375 --> 00:23:47,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大家讲道理嘛</font></font></font>

350
00:23:48,208 --> 00:23:49,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在我数三下</font></font></font>

351
00:23:49,083 --> 00:23:50,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你要说清楚你要不要</font></font></font>

352
00:23:53,958 --> 00:23:54,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空</font></font></font>

353
00:23:59,292 --> 00:24:00,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大家看到了</font></font></font>

354
00:24:00,708 --> 00:24:02,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这家伙没事就长篇大论，婆婆妈妈</font></font></font>

355
00:24:02,458 --> 00:24:03,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叽叽歪歪</font></font></font>

356
00:24:03,708 --> 00:24:05,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就活像整天一只苍蝇</font></font></font>

357
00:24:08,292 --> 00:24:09,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对不起，不是一只</font></font></font>

358
00:24:09,958 --> 00:24:12,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是一堆苍蝇围着你呀</font></font></font>

359
00:24:16,875 --> 00:24:19,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">飞到你的耳朵里面</font></font></font>

360
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:22,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀…</font></font></font>

361
00:24:23,917 --> 00:24:26,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀！</font></font></font>

362
00:24:34,458 --> 00:24:36,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以我就抓住这只苍蝇挤破它肚子</font></font></font>

363
00:24:36,458 --> 00:24:37,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把它肠子扯出来</font></font></font>

364
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:40,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再将它肠子缠着它脖子，用力一拉</font></font></font>

365
00:24:41,458 --> 00:24:44,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">整条舌头都伸出来了，我再手起刀落</font></font></font>

366
00:24:48,125 --> 00:24:50,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">整个世界清静了</font></font></font>

367
00:24:54,375 --> 00:24:55,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在大家知道</font></font></font>

368
00:24:57,792 --> 00:24:59,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我为什么要杀它了</font></font></font>

369
00:24:59,583 --> 00:25:00,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的吗？</font></font></font>

370
00:25:00,583 --> 00:25:01,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">诸多借口</font></font></font>

371
00:25:01,958 --> 00:25:03,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你根本不想去取西经</font></font></font>

372
00:25:03,792 --> 00:25:05,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不管怎么解释也不能原谅你</font></font></font>

373
00:25:05,958 --> 00:25:07,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">欺师灭祖的行为</font></font></font>

374
00:25:07,792 --> 00:25:08,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">姐姐</font></font></font>

375
00:25:10,125 --> 00:25:11,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这是你的不对了</font></font></font>

376
00:25:14,042 --> 00:25:15,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空他要吃我</font></font></font>

377
00:25:15,875 --> 00:25:17,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只不过是一个构思</font></font></font>

378
00:25:17,417 --> 00:25:18,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还没有成为一个事实</font></font></font>

379
00:25:19,417 --> 00:25:21,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又没有证据</font></font></font>

380
00:25:21,125 --> 00:25:22,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牠又何罪之有呢？</font></font></font>

381
00:25:23,333 --> 00:25:25,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不如等牠吃了我之后</font></font></font>

382
00:25:25,833 --> 00:25:29,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你有凭有据，再定牠的罪也不迟</font></font></font>

383
00:25:29,167 --> 00:25:31,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏，你啰嗦我早就听说过了</font></font></font>

384
00:25:32,042 --> 00:25:33,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过没想到你居然这么啰嗦</font></font></font>

385
00:25:33,917 --> 00:25:36,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我给你的金刚圈要你用来制服这猴子</font></font></font>

386
00:25:36,250 --> 00:25:37,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你居然不用</font></font></font>

387
00:25:38,083 --> 00:25:40,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那个金刚圈尺吋太差</font></font></font>

388
00:25:41,125 --> 00:25:43,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">前重后轻，左宽右窄</font></font></font>

389
00:25:43,708 --> 00:25:45,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他戴上之后很不舒服</font></font></font>

390
00:25:46,208 --> 00:25:48,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">整晚失眠，会连累我嘛</font></font></font>

391
00:25:49,208 --> 00:25:50,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牠虽然是个猴子</font></font></font>

392
00:25:50,792 --> 00:25:52,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是你也不能这样对牠呀</font></font></font>

393
00:25:52,875 --> 00:25:55,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">官府知道会说我虐待动物的</font></font></font>

394
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">讲起个金刚圈…</font></font></font>

395
00:25:58,208 --> 00:26:00,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去年我在陈家村认识了一位铁匠</font></font></font>

396
00:26:01,042 --> 00:26:03,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他手工精美，价钱又公道</font></font></font>

397
00:26:03,625 --> 00:26:04,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">童叟无欺</font></font></font>

398
00:26:05,083 --> 00:26:06,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干脆我介绍你</font></font></font>

399
00:26:06,417 --> 00:26:08,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再订造一个吧</font></font></font>

400
00:26:09,125 --> 00:26:10,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">闭嘴！</font></font></font>

401
00:26:10,125 --> 00:26:10,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">闭嘴！</font></font></font>

402
00:26:14,792 --> 00:26:16,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">罪过…</font></font></font>

403
00:26:18,125 --> 00:26:22,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在你们体会到我的痛苦了吧！</font></font></font>

404
00:26:24,083 --> 00:26:25,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">回答我！</font></font></font>

405
00:26:29,458 --> 00:26:30,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">搞定了</font></font></font>

406
00:26:33,417 --> 00:26:36,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我叫你不要乱扔东西了</font></font></font>

407
00:26:46,958 --> 00:26:48,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妖猴受死吧！</font></font></font>

408
00:26:52,292 --> 00:26:53,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">凭你也想收服我！</font></font></font>

409
00:26:53,583 --> 00:26:54,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为你是如来佛祖呀</font></font></font>

410
00:26:54,958 --> 00:26:56,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要打了…</font></font></font>

411
00:26:56,833 --> 00:26:57,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">观音姐姐</font></font></font>

412
00:26:57,875 --> 00:27:00,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">请你放过悟空，不要伤害牠啦</font></font></font>

413
00:27:03,833 --> 00:27:04,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们不要打了</font></font></font>

414
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天我要替天行道！</font></font></font>

415
00:27:22,417 --> 00:27:24,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">观音姐姐，手下留情呀</font></font></font>

416
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">试问人谁无过？</font></font></font>

417
00:27:26,250 --> 00:27:27,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牠总算是我的徒弟</font></font></font>

418
00:27:28,167 --> 00:27:30,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">徒弟有错，做师父也有责任</font></font></font>

419
00:27:30,417 --> 00:27:32,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">求观音姐姐放牠一条生路吧</font></font></font>

420
00:27:33,292 --> 00:27:34,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不消灭牠</font></font></font>

421
00:27:34,417 --> 00:27:36,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">无法向玉皇大帝交代</font></font></font>

422
00:27:36,583 --> 00:27:38,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不会使你为难的</font></font></font>

423
00:27:38,292 --> 00:27:40,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">请观音姐姐跟玉皇大帝说一声</font></font></font>

424
00:27:40,083 --> 00:27:42,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贫僧愿意一命赔一命</font></font></font>

425
00:27:43,667 --> 00:27:44,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">吓？</font></font></font>

426
00:27:47,042 --> 00:27:49,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">正所谓我不入地狱，谁入地狱呢？</font></font></font>

427
00:27:50,542 --> 00:27:51,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">求姐姐你体谅</font></font></font>

428
00:27:52,292 --> 00:27:55,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我这样做，无非是想感化劣徒</font></font></font>

429
00:27:56,333 --> 00:28:00,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以配合我佛慈悲的大无畏精神啊</font></font></font>

430
00:28:05,833 --> 00:28:07,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">善哉…</font></font></font>

431
00:28:07,292 --> 00:28:09,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，希望你有一天能够领悟到</font></font></font>

432
00:28:09,958 --> 00:28:12,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你师父这种舍身取义的精神</font></font></font>

433
00:28:21,958 --> 00:28:25,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喃呒阿弥陀佛</font></font></font>

434
00:28:47,667 --> 00:28:48,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道又做梦了？</font></font></font>

435
00:28:49,667 --> 00:28:50,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这次麻烦大了</font></font></font>

436
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:52,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有一次做的梦是好梦</font></font></font>

437
00:28:53,083 --> 00:28:54,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">青霞呢？</font></font></font>

438
00:28:54,292 --> 00:28:55,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没来过呀</font></font></font>

439
00:28:55,833 --> 00:28:57,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">青霞…</font></font></font>

440
00:29:00,958 --> 00:29:03,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">各位兄台，大家好吗？</font></font></font>

441
00:29:03,833 --> 00:29:04,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天气好冷啊！</font></font></font>

442
00:29:04,875 --> 00:29:05,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有没有多穿件衣服啊！</font></font></font>

443
00:29:05,917 --> 00:29:07,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小弟一时迷失方向</font></font></font>

444
00:29:07,083 --> 00:29:08,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想借个地方宿一个晚上</font></font></font>

445
00:29:09,125 --> 00:29:11,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">马屁精，到那边睡觉</font></font></font>

446
00:29:11,208 --> 00:29:12,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真是出门遇贵人</font></font></font>

447
00:29:12,333 --> 00:29:13,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祝大家万寿无疆啊，谢谢</font></font></font>

448
00:29:19,250 --> 00:29:20,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明明看见大师兄上山来了嘛</font></font></font>

449
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么人不见了？</font></font></font>

450
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:24,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">都是你害的，尿什么尿嘛！</font></font></font>

451
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:25,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">忍忍会憋死呀</font></font></font>

452
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">尿尿也犯法呀？</font></font></font>

453
00:29:40,958 --> 00:29:42,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">黑山老妖？</font></font></font>

454
00:30:10,250 --> 00:30:10,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空</font></font></font>

455
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:13,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又扮人样啦</font></font></font>

456
00:30:13,875 --> 00:30:15,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还认得为师吗？</font></font></font>

457
00:30:16,208 --> 00:30:17,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">又是你这只苍蝇</font></font></font>

458
00:30:17,875 --> 00:30:18,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空…</font></font></font>

459
00:30:20,875 --> 00:30:22,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不可能，一定是在作梦</font></font></font>

460
00:30:23,042 --> 00:30:26,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空要作梦还早着呢，不过…</font></font></font>

461
00:30:27,375 --> 00:30:29,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我在时空穿梭的时候</font></font></font>

462
00:30:29,375 --> 00:30:31,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">经常在梦里见到你</font></font></font>

463
00:30:31,708 --> 00:30:33,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你是不是很想念为师啊？</font></font></font>

464
00:30:33,667 --> 00:30:35,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对了，那月光宝盒是否在你哪儿啊？</font></font></font>

465
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:38,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是在我这儿，你还想要？</font></font></font>

466
00:30:38,542 --> 00:30:39,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是谁啊？</font></font></font>

467
00:30:42,333 --> 00:30:43,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么事呀？　﹣有官兵啊！</font></font></font>

468
00:30:44,250 --> 00:30:45,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有官兵</font></font></font>

469
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:48,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他也想在这儿借宿一晚，是我老爸</font></font></font>

470
00:30:48,583 --> 00:30:49,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没问题吧！</font></font></font>

471
00:30:50,625 --> 00:30:51,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你老爸！</font></font></font>

472
00:30:51,708 --> 00:30:55,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊，老爸，出来跟诸位大哥打招呼</font></font></font>

473
00:30:56,750 --> 00:30:57,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他哪儿来的？</font></font></font>

474
00:30:59,042 --> 00:31:00,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">印度来的</font></font></font>

475
00:31:00,208 --> 00:31:02,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">印度？怎么没听过？</font></font></font>

476
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:04,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们明天还要赶路，你睡那边吧！</font></font></font>

477
00:31:04,792 --> 00:31:05,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">多谢</font></font></font>

478
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:07,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真吵死人了</font></font></font>

479
00:31:08,042 --> 00:31:09,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">烦不烦呀？</font></font></font>

480
00:31:10,417 --> 00:31:11,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">睡里面</font></font></font>

481
00:31:11,958 --> 00:31:13,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真要命啊，时差不对</font></font></font>

482
00:31:13,917 --> 00:31:15,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">刚刚才从印度那边才睡醒又要我睡</font></font></font>

483
00:31:16,042 --> 00:31:17,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要你睡就睡啦</font></font></font>

484
00:31:17,167 --> 00:31:18,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒在哪里？</font></font></font>

485
00:31:18,292 --> 00:31:20,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，你斯文点不行</font></font></font>

486
00:31:20,875 --> 00:31:24,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么老是那么猴急呢？你看</font></font></font>

487
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:54,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他在干什么？</font></font></font>

488
00:31:54,542 --> 00:31:56,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他在吸阳气啊</font></font></font>

489
00:31:56,417 --> 00:31:57,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">装睡吧！</font></font></font>

490
00:31:57,417 --> 00:31:59,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望他吸饱了别人就不吸我们了</font></font></font>

491
00:31:59,292 --> 00:32:00,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快睡啊！</font></font></font>

492
00:33:12,208 --> 00:33:13,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走呀！</font></font></font>

493
00:33:21,583 --> 00:33:22,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不认得我了</font></font></font>

494
00:33:24,292 --> 00:33:25,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">刚刚那印度阿三…</font></font></font>

495
00:33:26,958 --> 00:33:29,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你喜欢啊，拿去吧！</font></font></font>

496
00:33:29,417 --> 00:33:30,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我徒弟叫我了bye bye</font></font></font>

497
00:33:38,125 --> 00:33:39,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我叫你不要玩火了嘛</font></font></font>

498
00:33:39,708 --> 00:33:41,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">阿弥陀佛 goodbye</font></font></font>

499
00:33:42,125 --> 00:33:44,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我又不认识你们拜托不要跟着我们</font></font></font>

500
00:33:45,958 --> 00:33:48,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师父能够见到你真好了</font></font></font>

501
00:33:48,250 --> 00:33:50,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那个盒子呢？盒子呢？</font></font></font>

502
00:33:54,542 --> 00:33:55,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">又是牛魔王？</font></font></font>

503
00:33:56,292 --> 00:33:59,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贤弟，你把唐僧抓来给我啦…</font></font></font>

504
00:34:10,667 --> 00:34:12,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">恭喜！恭喜！</font></font></font>

505
00:34:17,250 --> 00:34:18,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小姐，毛巾</font></font></font>

506
00:34:20,833 --> 00:34:23,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">结婚嘛，你哭什么哭？</font></font></font>

507
00:34:23,667 --> 00:34:27,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不是哭，我看到你流口水嘛</font></font></font>

508
00:34:36,375 --> 00:34:37,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天是双喜临门</font></font></font>

509
00:34:38,333 --> 00:34:39,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么？</font></font></font>

510
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天除了舍妹出阁之日</font></font></font>

511
00:34:43,208 --> 00:34:46,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也是我雄牛纳妾之时</font></font></font>

512
00:34:46,625 --> 00:34:48,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说纳妾？</font></font></font>

513
00:34:48,625 --> 00:34:49,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那大嫂没有意见吗？</font></font></font>

514
00:34:50,042 --> 00:34:51,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">呸，那黄脸婆</font></font></font>

515
00:34:51,583 --> 00:34:53,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在在十万九千里外的火焰山里</font></font></font>

516
00:34:53,417 --> 00:34:55,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算她知道也奈何不了我</font></font></font>

517
00:34:57,375 --> 00:34:59,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牛大哥你能说你怎么认识</font></font></font>

518
00:34:59,833 --> 00:35:01,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这位新夫人呀？</font></font></font>

519
00:35:04,292 --> 00:35:06,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我前天路过洛阳沙漠</font></font></font>

520
00:35:06,792 --> 00:35:09,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看到一个貌美如花的女子</font></font></font>

521
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:11,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">趴在地上奄奄一息</font></font></font>

522
00:35:11,417 --> 00:35:12,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大师兄，现在怎么办？</font></font></font>

523
00:35:12,833 --> 00:35:14,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好了啦！没问题啦…</font></font></font>

524
00:35:14,542 --> 00:35:17,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的没问题啦，哟！我们这次成功了</font></font></font>

525
00:35:17,417 --> 00:35:21,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞你的名字太好听了</font></font></font>

526
00:35:23,875 --> 00:35:27,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来…我来介绍我妹妹和妹夫给你认识</font></font></font>

527
00:35:28,042 --> 00:35:29,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">香香，贤弟</font></font></font>

528
00:35:31,333 --> 00:35:32,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来…跟我来</font></font></font>

529
00:35:38,583 --> 00:35:39,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个呢是我妹夫</font></font></font>

530
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这是我妹妹香香</font></font></font>

531
00:35:42,500 --> 00:35:43,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞姑娘</font></font></font>

532
00:35:50,167 --> 00:35:51,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你能留在这里成亲吗？</font></font></font>

533
00:35:52,708 --> 00:35:53,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可以吧！</font></font></font>

534
00:35:55,458 --> 00:35:56,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你家里的老婆怎么办？</font></font></font>

535
00:35:57,708 --> 00:35:59,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">老婆？你们两个认识吗？</font></font></font>

536
00:36:02,583 --> 00:36:03,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你有老婆？</font></font></font>

537
00:36:03,792 --> 00:36:05,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">已经离婚了</font></font></font>

538
00:36:05,125 --> 00:36:07,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么我从来就没有听你说过呢？</font></font></font>

539
00:36:07,708 --> 00:36:09,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎…妹妹</font></font></font>

540
00:36:09,542 --> 00:36:12,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">男人有三妻四妾很平常嘛</font></font></font>

541
00:36:12,958 --> 00:36:14,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别那么紧张</font></font></font>

542
00:36:14,625 --> 00:36:16,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贤弟，你说对不对？</font></font></font>

543
00:36:17,708 --> 00:36:18,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对…</font></font></font>

544
00:36:19,958 --> 00:36:21,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞，实不相瞒</font></font></font>

545
00:36:21,708 --> 00:36:23,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">经过这两天朝夕相处</font></font></font>

546
00:36:23,583 --> 00:36:25,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我发觉我已经深深的爱上你</font></font></font>

547
00:36:26,208 --> 00:36:27,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为了表示对你的诚意</font></font></font>

548
00:36:28,167 --> 00:36:30,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我当着这么多兄弟面前向你求婚</font></font></font>

549
00:36:30,292 --> 00:36:31,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个月光宝盒</font></font></font>

550
00:36:31,833 --> 00:36:33,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是我送给你的订情信物</font></font></font>

551
00:36:33,667 --> 00:36:35,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望你能嫁给我</font></font></font>

552
00:36:36,292 --> 00:36:38,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我反对这门亲事！</font></font></font>

553
00:36:38,125 --> 00:36:38,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

554
00:36:38,792 --> 00:36:40,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">让我来，说什么…</font></font></font>

555
00:36:40,583 --> 00:36:42,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">人家郎才女貌，天生一对</font></font></font>

556
00:36:42,417 --> 00:36:44,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">轮到你这妖怪来反对啊？</font></font></font>

557
00:36:44,542 --> 00:36:47,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞仙子择偶是有一个规矩的</font></font></font>

558
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:49,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果大哥你能做得到</font></font></font>

559
00:36:49,792 --> 00:36:51,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们就心服口服</font></font></font>

560
00:36:51,292 --> 00:36:52,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有什么规矩啊？</font></font></font>

561
00:36:52,625 --> 00:36:54,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她曾经发誓</font></font></font>

562
00:36:54,750 --> 00:36:58,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果谁能把紫青宝剑拔出鞘的话</font></font></font>

563
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是她的如意中人</font></font></font>

564
00:37:04,042 --> 00:37:05,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫青宝剑</font></font></font>

565
00:37:06,292 --> 00:37:07,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">让我来</font></font></font>

566
00:37:09,167 --> 00:37:10,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有这种事</font></font></font>

567
00:37:10,917 --> 00:37:13,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个只不过是我跟大家开的一个玩笑</font></font></font>

568
00:37:13,292 --> 00:37:14,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">开玩笑？</font></font></font>

569
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这把剑谁拔得出，谁拔不出</font></font></font>

570
00:37:17,875 --> 00:37:18,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">根本没有关系</font></font></font>

571
00:37:22,583 --> 00:37:24,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们这些混蛋在我地盘瞎搞和？</font></font></font>

572
00:37:25,417 --> 00:37:26,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁敢阻止我谁就死</font></font></font>

573
00:37:34,333 --> 00:37:36,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁敢阻止我，我就杀了谁</font></font></font>

574
00:37:38,583 --> 00:37:40,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大王，铁扇公主来了</font></font></font>

575
00:37:46,958 --> 00:37:48,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎！你怎么躲在这里啊？</font></font></font>

576
00:37:50,667 --> 00:37:52,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当时那把剑离我喉咙</font></font></font>

577
00:37:52,083 --> 00:37:53,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只有零点零一公分</font></font></font>

578
00:37:54,125 --> 00:37:55,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">但是四分之一柱香之后</font></font></font>

579
00:37:55,625 --> 00:37:58,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那把剑的女主人将会彻底的爱上我</font></font></font>

580
00:37:58,208 --> 00:37:59,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为我决定说一个谎话</font></font></font>

581
00:38:00,083 --> 00:38:02,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">虽然本人生平说了无数的谎话</font></font></font>

582
00:38:02,375 --> 00:38:05,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">但是这一个，我认为是最完美的</font></font></font>

583
00:38:07,375 --> 00:38:09,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你再往前半步，我就把你给杀了</font></font></font>

584
00:38:10,292 --> 00:38:11,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你应该这么做</font></font></font>

585
00:38:12,625 --> 00:38:14,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也应该死</font></font></font>

586
00:38:15,417 --> 00:38:18,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">曾经有一份真诚的爱情放在我面前</font></font></font>

587
00:38:19,417 --> 00:38:20,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我没有珍惜</font></font></font>

588
00:38:21,375 --> 00:38:22,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等我失去的时候</font></font></font>

589
00:38:23,583 --> 00:38:25,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我才后悔莫及</font></font></font>

590
00:38:27,042 --> 00:38:30,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">人世间最痛苦的事莫过于此</font></font></font>

591
00:38:31,792 --> 00:38:34,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的剑在我的咽喉上割下去吧！</font></font></font>

592
00:38:35,333 --> 00:38:36,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用再犹豫了</font></font></font>

593
00:38:39,292 --> 00:38:40,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果上天能够给我一个</font></font></font>

594
00:38:40,833 --> 00:38:42,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再来一次的机会</font></font></font>

595
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:45,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我会对那个女孩说三个字</font></font></font>

596
00:38:47,958 --> 00:38:49,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我爱你</font></font></font>

597
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:54,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果非要在这份爱上面加一个期限</font></font></font>

598
00:38:57,458 --> 00:38:59,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我希望是一万年</font></font></font>

599
00:39:12,750 --> 00:39:15,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么你怎么向你娘子交代？</font></font></font>

600
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一定要交代</font></font></font>

601
00:39:18,125 --> 00:39:19,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以我一定要拿回那个月光宝盒</font></font></font>

602
00:39:20,250 --> 00:39:22,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">带你一起回去，跟她们说清楚</font></font></font>

603
00:39:24,292 --> 00:39:25,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不管别人怎么说我</font></font></font>

604
00:39:26,917 --> 00:39:29,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也不怕后世会有千千万万的人</font></font></font>

605
00:39:29,708 --> 00:39:30,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对我唾骂</font></font></font>

606
00:39:33,125 --> 00:39:34,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一个人承担下来</font></font></font>

607
00:39:36,083 --> 00:39:37,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要骗我吧！</font></font></font>

608
00:39:38,042 --> 00:39:41,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">但是我痛恨我自己没本事</font></font></font>

609
00:39:41,583 --> 00:39:42,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去拿回那个月光宝盒</font></font></font>

610
00:39:44,208 --> 00:39:45,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我　﹣我帮你</font></font></font>

611
00:39:46,042 --> 00:39:47,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要！太危险了</font></font></font>

612
00:39:48,083 --> 00:39:48,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不想</font></font></font>

613
00:39:50,708 --> 00:39:51,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想</font></font></font>

614
00:39:51,667 --> 00:39:53,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我怎么会金屋藏娇呢</font></font></font>

615
00:39:53,833 --> 00:39:54,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谣言啊，夫人</font></font></font>

616
00:39:54,792 --> 00:39:55,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">鬼才相信你…</font></font></font>

617
00:39:57,708 --> 00:39:58,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们在这儿你干什么？</font></font></font>

618
00:40:05,042 --> 00:40:05,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他是谁啊？</font></font></font>

619
00:40:09,458 --> 00:40:11,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我问你啊，他是谁啊？</font></font></font>

620
00:40:12,333 --> 00:40:13,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他</font></font></font>

621
00:40:13,625 --> 00:40:15,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贤弟，他是谁啊？你说呀</font></font></font>

622
00:40:15,625 --> 00:40:17,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他是我的发妻</font></font></font>

623
00:40:17,792 --> 00:40:20,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！贤弟你太过份了</font></font></font>

624
00:40:20,250 --> 00:40:21,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好哥们</font></font></font>

625
00:40:21,583 --> 00:40:22,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你居然还把妹妹嫁给他？</font></font></font>

626
00:40:23,375 --> 00:40:26,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以他老婆也看不过去，用剑指他呀</font></font></font>

627
00:40:27,083 --> 00:40:29,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你跟我过来，我有话要问你</font></font></font>

628
00:40:30,250 --> 00:40:31,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来你有老婆呀</font></font></font>

629
00:40:31,833 --> 00:40:33,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">感情破裂了</font></font></font>

630
00:40:33,250 --> 00:40:35,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你跟我说清楚到底发生什么事</font></font></font>

631
00:40:36,458 --> 00:40:37,541
