<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上天真的这么安排</font></font></font>

755
00:47:50,333 --> 00:47:51,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那我也没有办法</font></font></font>

756
00:47:53,125 --> 00:47:54,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！</font></font></font>

757
00:47:55,125 --> 00:47:56,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用上天安排</font></font></font>

758
00:47:58,875 --> 00:47:59,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想干什么？</font></font></font>

759
00:48:08,708 --> 00:48:09,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走，走…</font></font></font>

760
00:48:11,083 --> 00:48:12,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">移形换影大法！</font></font></font>

761
00:48:20,083 --> 00:48:21,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要把你跟石头调换</font></font></font>

762
00:48:22,625 --> 00:48:23,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放开我！</font></font></font>

763
00:48:26,458 --> 00:48:27,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的胸部啊！</font></font></font>

764
00:49:00,208 --> 00:49:02,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞…！</font></font></font>

765
00:49:02,667 --> 00:49:03,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你醒醒</font></font></font>

766
00:49:05,250 --> 00:49:07,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大师兄，你干嘛搂着我啊？</font></font></font>

767
00:49:10,083 --> 00:49:10,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">猪八戒？</font></font></font>

768
00:49:11,625 --> 00:49:12,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是呀！</font></font></font>

769
00:49:13,042 --> 00:49:13,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那紫霞呢？</font></font></font>

770
00:49:13,958 --> 00:49:14,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">秦祥林…</font></font></font>

771
00:49:19,125 --> 00:49:19,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">青霞？</font></font></font>

772
00:49:22,625 --> 00:49:24,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个玩笑开大了吧</font></font></font>

773
00:49:24,250 --> 00:49:27,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">完了…！连我也中招了</font></font></font>

774
00:49:27,792 --> 00:49:29,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我两块胸肌都掉到肚脐上了</font></font></font>

775
00:49:32,458 --> 00:49:33,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不会嫌弃我吧？</font></font></font>

776
00:49:34,667 --> 00:49:35,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当然不会</font></font></font>

777
00:49:40,250 --> 00:49:41,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你明明就是嫌弃我</font></font></font>

778
00:49:41,292 --> 00:49:42,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！从此一刀两断</font></font></font>

779
00:49:44,000 --> 00:49:44,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">给多一点时间</font></font></font>

780
00:49:45,333 --> 00:49:46,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我吐哇吐哇的就会习惯了</font></font></font>

781
00:49:49,833 --> 00:49:51,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！我相信你</font></font></font>

782
00:49:51,125 --> 00:49:52,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我给你一点时间</font></font></font>

783
00:49:52,542 --> 00:49:54,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等你吐惯了再说</font></font></font>

784
00:49:56,250 --> 00:49:57,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我习惯了</font></font></font>

785
00:49:58,833 --> 00:49:59,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别再说了</font></font></font>

786
00:49:59,708 --> 00:50:00,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">连我都想吐啦</font></font></font>

787
00:50:02,625 --> 00:50:04,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">都怪你！长得跟猪一样</font></font></font>

788
00:50:04,125 --> 00:50:06,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要不然的话他会吐成这样子吗？</font></font></font>

789
00:50:15,042 --> 00:50:16,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他为我着想</font></font></font>

790
00:50:16,083 --> 00:50:17,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我决定嫁给他</font></font></font>

791
00:50:17,292 --> 00:50:18,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要给他一个温暖的家庭</font></font></font>

792
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:20,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为他生很多很多小孩子</font></font></font>

793
00:50:22,750 --> 00:50:23,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祥林！</font></font></font>

794
00:50:29,292 --> 00:50:30,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要杀了你！</font></font></font>

795
00:50:31,125 --> 00:50:31,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">杀了你！</font></font></font>

796
00:50:32,042 --> 00:50:35,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师弟，你也中招了？</font></font></font>

797
00:50:37,208 --> 00:50:38,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你快给我换过来</font></font></font>

798
00:50:38,750 --> 00:50:39,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别吵！</font></font></font>

799
00:50:39,375 --> 00:50:42,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">告诉你，不为难你</font></font></font>

800
00:50:42,375 --> 00:50:44,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你赶快发功，把我们换回来</font></font></font>

801
00:50:44,417 --> 00:50:45,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为我不想吗？</font></font></font>

802
00:50:45,417 --> 00:50:46,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">发一次功要等七七四十九天以后</font></font></font>

803
00:50:46,958 --> 00:50:48,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">才能发第二次的嘛</font></font></font>

804
00:50:48,125 --> 00:50:50,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">七七四十九天以后？我…</font></font></font>

805
00:50:50,250 --> 00:50:52,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祥林，你面对现实吧！</font></font></font>

806
00:50:55,625 --> 00:50:56,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不快发功，我要你好看</font></font></font>

807
00:50:57,500 --> 00:50:59,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快发功！少装蒜！</font></font></font>

808
00:51:00,083 --> 00:51:00,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快点！</font></font></font>

809
00:51:02,375 --> 00:51:03,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁在我里面啊？</font></font></font>

810
00:51:04,208 --> 00:51:05,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁在你里面？我也不知道我自己在哪</font></font></font>

811
00:51:06,292 --> 00:51:07,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两个声音？　﹣你是谁？</font></font></font>

812
00:51:07,583 --> 00:51:09,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是猪八戒啊，你呢？</font></font></font>

813
00:51:09,250 --> 00:51:10,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是紫霞</font></font></font>

814
00:51:12,875 --> 00:51:13,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祥林</font></font></font>

815
00:51:14,833 --> 00:51:15,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">至尊宝</font></font></font>

816
00:51:15,750 --> 00:51:16,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师兄</font></font></font>

817
00:51:19,333 --> 00:51:20,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞</font></font></font>

818
00:51:22,417 --> 00:51:23,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞，你还在这里？</font></font></font>

819
00:51:23,958 --> 00:51:25,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这个贱人</font></font></font>

820
00:51:27,208 --> 00:51:28,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">终于被我看到你了</font></font></font>

821
00:51:29,042 --> 00:51:29,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么啦？</font></font></font>

822
00:51:29,917 --> 00:51:31,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没见多久怎么变成这个样子啊？</font></font></font>

823
00:51:32,333 --> 00:51:33,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒呢？</font></font></font>

824
00:51:34,125 --> 00:51:35,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">忘了拿啦</font></font></font>

825
00:51:37,333 --> 00:51:38,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">骗你的</font></font></font>

826
00:51:40,375 --> 00:51:41,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">拿来</font></font></font>

827
00:51:41,500 --> 00:51:42,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你拿月光宝盒干什么？</font></font></font>

828
00:51:42,875 --> 00:51:43,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跟我远走高飞呀</font></font></font>

829
00:51:43,917 --> 00:51:45,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要缠着他，肥婆！</font></font></font>

830
00:51:47,292 --> 00:51:50,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祥林会跟你远走高…牛魔王</font></font></font>

831
00:51:53,875 --> 00:51:55,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">少在那做白日梦</font></font></font>

832
00:51:56,208 --> 00:51:57,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不信啊，你问问他！</font></font></font>

833
00:51:59,417 --> 00:52:00,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说喜欢我</font></font></font>

834
00:52:00,708 --> 00:52:01,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是为了拿这个跟她远走高飞</font></font></font>

835
00:52:02,042 --> 00:52:02,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是不是？　﹣等等…</font></font></font>

836
00:52:03,917 --> 00:52:05,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">完全没这回事</font></font></font>

837
00:52:07,167 --> 00:52:08,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不信你扔掉这块烂东西吧！</font></font></font>

838
00:52:09,208 --> 00:52:10,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！</font></font></font>

839
00:52:11,083 --> 00:52:12,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">做人干嘛那么认真，冲动呢</font></font></font>

840
00:52:13,458 --> 00:52:14,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看你那副贱相</font></font></font>

841
00:52:14,667 --> 00:52:15,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还说不是？</font></font></font>

842
00:52:15,708 --> 00:52:16,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就扔掉它</font></font></font>

843
00:52:27,500 --> 00:52:28,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哥哥…</font></font></font>

844
00:52:30,458 --> 00:52:31,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好有男子气慨！</font></font></font>

845
00:52:31,458 --> 00:52:32,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">闭咀！</font></font></font>

846
00:52:34,292 --> 00:52:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我很喜欢</font></font></font>

847
00:52:36,292 --> 00:52:38,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看你们能到哪儿去！</font></font></font>

848
00:52:39,583 --> 00:52:41,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牛兄，你怎么伤成这样？</font></font></font>

849
00:52:42,875 --> 00:52:44,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为那黄脸婆，比我伤得轻吗？</font></font></font>

850
00:52:45,542 --> 00:52:46,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看看！</font></font></font>

851
00:52:47,583 --> 00:52:48,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你骗得我好惨啊</font></font></font>

852
00:52:49,542 --> 00:52:50,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">其实我根本就不是</font></font></font>

853
00:52:50,917 --> 00:52:52,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">祥林，她是谁呀？</font></font></font>

854
00:52:53,333 --> 00:52:54,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我相信你才怪！</font></font></font>

855
00:52:55,000 --> 00:52:56,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">混蛋！我们现在正式离婚</font></font></font>

856
00:52:56,875 --> 00:52:57,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以后谁也别管谁！</font></font></font>

857
00:52:58,167 --> 00:53:00,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！你要我的！我要我的！</font></font></font>

858
00:53:02,750 --> 00:53:04,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快点救紫霞，肉身你也有份的</font></font></font>

859
00:53:24,083 --> 00:53:25,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">打得血肉模糊的，拿回来也没用啦</font></font></font>

860
00:53:26,042 --> 00:53:26,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对！</font></font></font>

861
00:53:29,625 --> 00:53:30,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想跑？</font></font></font>

862
00:53:32,167 --> 00:53:33,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天说清楚别走！</font></font></font>

863
00:53:33,958 --> 00:53:35,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不准打他！</font></font></font>

864
00:53:36,583 --> 00:53:37,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">死肥婆</font></font></font>

865
00:53:37,625 --> 00:53:38,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我跟他的事用不着你帮忙？</font></font></font>

866
00:53:39,417 --> 00:53:40,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">省省吧！</font></font></font>

867
00:53:40,458 --> 00:53:41,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是怕他打坏我的肉身</font></font></font>

868
00:53:44,708 --> 00:53:45,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">鬼才有空帮你</font></font></font>

869
00:53:46,083 --> 00:53:47,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">打就打，那么多废话干嘛？</font></font></font>

870
00:53:47,667 --> 00:53:49,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当心我帮他一起打你呀</font></font></font>

871
00:53:50,542 --> 00:53:51,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你试试看！</font></font></font>

872
00:53:51,583 --> 00:53:54,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是女人，玩真的，我跟你拼了</font></font></font>

873
00:54:03,167 --> 00:54:04,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就不帮你们，看你们打多久</font></font></font>

874
00:54:05,333 --> 00:54:05,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快走</font></font></font>

875
00:54:06,042 --> 00:54:06,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不行</font></font></font>

876
00:54:06,917 --> 00:54:08,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一定要帮你把月光宝盒拿回来</font></font></font>

877
00:54:08,375 --> 00:54:09,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好让你跟你娘子有个交待</font></font></font>

878
00:54:10,333 --> 00:54:12,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这个人真讲义气，没话说</font></font></font>

879
00:54:12,250 --> 00:54:12,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的？</font></font></font>

880
00:54:13,000 --> 00:54:14,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你都这么做了，我还有什么话说？</font></font></font>

881
00:54:22,042 --> 00:54:22,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等等！</font></font></font>

882
00:54:33,833 --> 00:54:34,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你！</font></font></font>

883
00:54:35,542 --> 00:54:37,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">黄脸婆，别打我马子</font></font></font>

884
00:54:37,583 --> 00:54:38,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我喜欢</font></font></font>

885
00:54:40,750 --> 00:54:42,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的小白脸跑了</font></font></font>

886
00:54:44,625 --> 00:54:45,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跑都跑得那么帅</font></font></font>

887
00:54:46,083 --> 00:54:47,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我真幸福</font></font></font>

888
00:54:55,708 --> 00:54:57,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没办法，假装跳一下吧！</font></font></font>

889
00:55:01,958 --> 00:55:03,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">摆近一点比较像</font></font></font>

890
00:55:07,167 --> 00:55:08,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空</font></font></font>

891
00:55:08,500 --> 00:55:09,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别跳下去啊！</font></font></font>

892
00:55:11,583 --> 00:55:13,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">鬼才想跳啦！</font></font></font>

893
00:55:13,458 --> 00:55:15,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你宁愿跳悬崖也不肯见我</font></font></font>

894
00:55:15,958 --> 00:55:17,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">算了，我还是回火焰山吧！</font></font></font>

895
00:55:23,750 --> 00:55:25,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早知道要充军的话</font></font></font>

896
00:55:25,333 --> 00:55:26,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们就不做这件案子啦！</font></font></font>

897
00:55:27,917 --> 00:55:31,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁知道偷葡萄会那么大罪要充军呢？</font></font></font>

898
00:55:31,750 --> 00:55:34,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早知道这样就不要做贼啦嘛</font></font></font>

899
00:55:34,458 --> 00:55:35,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早知道就别做贼！</font></font></font>

900
00:55:35,542 --> 00:55:36,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">像我这样当兵</font></font></font>

901
00:55:36,750 --> 00:55:38,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们没有机会了</font></font></font>

902
00:55:38,125 --> 00:55:39,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">除非神仙来救你们</font></font></font>

903
00:55:51,000 --> 00:55:53,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早知道不当兵了</font></font></font>

904
00:55:59,958 --> 00:56:01,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真有神仙来救了</font></font></font>

905
00:56:01,958 --> 00:56:03,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神仙啊！</font></font></font>

906
00:56:06,583 --> 00:56:07,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶！</font></font></font>

907
00:56:19,333 --> 00:56:20,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提大哥啊</font></font></font>

908
00:56:20,375 --> 00:56:21,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他蒸呀蒸的又想蒸馒头呀</font></font></font>

909
00:56:21,792 --> 00:56:22,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你别多事啦！</font></font></font>

910
00:56:23,583 --> 00:56:24,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶！</font></font></font>

911
00:56:31,375 --> 00:56:33,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎，你别再吃我豆腐！</font></font></font>

912
00:56:34,250 --> 00:56:36,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">人家喜欢你才吃你豆腐嘛</font></font></font>

913
00:56:37,208 --> 00:56:39,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">听着，你要做我的女人</font></font></font>

914
00:56:40,167 --> 00:56:42,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以后就别像你哥那样，为非作歹</font></font></font>

915
00:56:42,875 --> 00:56:43,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">知道了！</font></font></font>

916
00:56:44,625 --> 00:56:45,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走吧！</font></font></font>

917
00:56:46,042 --> 00:56:47,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喝茶！</font></font></font>

918
00:56:47,333 --> 00:56:48,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">麻烦你了！</font></font></font>

919
00:56:49,125 --> 00:56:50,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要客气！</font></font></font>

920
00:56:54,167 --> 00:56:55,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唉！为什么带我回这个洞来？</font></font></font>

921
00:56:56,042 --> 00:56:57,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是我带你来的</font></font></font>

922
00:56:57,542 --> 00:57:00,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你昏倒迷迷糊糊带我们来的</font></font></font>

923
00:57:02,875 --> 00:57:04,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一定是太想念晶晶了</font></font></font>

924
00:57:04,708 --> 00:57:06,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊！你昏倒的时候</font></font></font>

925
00:57:06,542 --> 00:57:08,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叫晶晶这个名字叫了九十八次</font></font></font>

926
00:57:12,542 --> 00:57:13,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶是我娘子</font></font></font>

927
00:57:13,958 --> 00:57:15,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还有一个名字叫紫霞的</font></font></font>

928
00:57:15,875 --> 00:57:17,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你叫了七百八十四次</font></font></font>

929
00:57:19,750 --> 00:57:21,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">七百八十四次</font></font></font>

930
00:57:21,250 --> 00:57:23,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这紫霞一定欠你很多钱</font></font></font>

931
00:57:24,833 --> 00:57:26,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要拜盘丝大仙为师</font></font></font>

932
00:57:26,833 --> 00:57:29,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她分明把水濂洞改为盘丝洞</font></font></font>

933
00:57:29,125 --> 00:57:30,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们竟敢骗我说没这个人？</font></font></font>

934
00:57:33,250 --> 00:57:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">臭猴子，原来你还在这儿！</font></font></font>

935
00:57:35,917 --> 00:57:36,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你为什么这样对我？</font></font></font>

936
00:57:38,792 --> 00:57:39,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶</font></font></font>

937
00:57:45,333 --> 00:57:47,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶，再看到你太好了</font></font></font>

938
00:57:47,625 --> 00:57:48,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？</font></font></font>

939
00:57:50,292 --> 00:57:51,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你瘦了</font></font></font>

940
00:57:53,375 --> 00:57:54,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不是孙悟空呀</font></font></font>

941
00:57:55,292 --> 00:57:56,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">但是我不知道怎么告诉你</font></font></font>

942
00:57:56,417 --> 00:57:57,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为你一定不会相信我</font></font></font>

943
00:57:58,167 --> 00:57:58,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我相信</font></font></font>

944
00:58:00,125 --> 00:58:01,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为那个臭猴子不会对我这么温柔</font></font></font>

945
00:58:02,833 --> 00:58:03,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你到底是谁？</font></font></font>

946
00:58:06,083 --> 00:58:07,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就是你五百年后的老公</font></font></font>

947
00:58:07,458 --> 00:58:08,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年后</font></font></font>

948
00:58:08,208 --> 00:58:09,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你会因为我而放弃现在这段感情</font></font></font>

949
00:58:09,625 --> 00:58:11,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我千辛万苦回这里和做的所有事情</font></font></font>

950
00:58:11,667 --> 00:58:12,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">完全都是为了你</font></font></font>

951
00:58:12,667 --> 00:58:13,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶，我想念你</font></font></font>

952
00:58:13,625 --> 00:58:14,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我真的很想念你</font></font></font>

953
00:58:14,667 --> 00:58:15,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我太想念你了</font></font></font>

954
00:58:17,208 --> 00:58:18,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喂！你相不相信？</font></font></font>

955
00:58:18,125 --> 00:58:18,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不相信！</font></font></font>

956
00:58:19,750 --> 00:58:20,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这也不能怪你，我看看怎么回事</font></font></font>

957
00:58:21,000 --> 00:58:22,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过我觉得我认识你</font></font></font>

958
00:58:23,750 --> 00:58:24,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">绝对认识</font></font></font>

959
00:58:25,583 --> 00:58:26,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">而且很熟</font></font></font>

960
00:58:27,083 --> 00:58:28,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">非常的熟！</font></font></font>

961
00:58:29,208 --> 00:58:32,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年之后，我们怎么认识的？</font></font></font>

962
00:58:34,750 --> 00:58:36,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在一个月黑风高阴森恐怖的晚上</font></font></font>

963
00:58:36,250 --> 00:58:37,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是至尊宝，你是白晶晶</font></font></font>

964
00:58:38,042 --> 00:58:39,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">奇妙的爱情</font></font></font>

965
00:58:39,083 --> 00:58:40,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就从桥头上的这一点火开始的</font></font></font>

966
00:58:41,833 --> 00:58:43,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我才一转过身你就突如奇来向我一指</font></font></font>

967
00:58:43,583 --> 00:58:44,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的整只手就着火了</font></font></font>

968
00:58:44,625 --> 00:58:46,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还要冲过来向我打</font></font></font>

969
00:58:46,625 --> 00:58:47,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">拼命的打…！</font></font></font>

970
00:58:48,000 --> 00:58:49,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是不是，不是这样打</font></font></font>

971
00:58:49,250 --> 00:58:50,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是这样，这样…</font></font></font>

972
00:58:50,708 --> 00:58:52,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啦，就是这样打你看到了吗？</font></font></font>

973
00:58:53,708 --> 00:58:55,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以后的发展我可以用一句</font></font></font>

974
00:58:55,083 --> 00:58:56,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">峰回路转来形容</font></font></font>

975
00:58:56,375 --> 00:58:57,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为突然之间杀出一个牛魔王</font></font></font>

976
00:58:58,667 --> 00:59:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当时你手拿一条龙骨大战牛魔王之后</font></font></font>

977
00:59:01,083 --> 00:59:02,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还把我抓到盘丝洞里去</font></font></font>

978
00:59:05,333 --> 00:59:07,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所谓光阴似箭真的一点也不错</font></font></font>

979
00:59:07,125 --> 00:59:08,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为才一转眼就说到重点了</font></font></font>

980
00:59:09,500 --> 00:59:11,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在断崖顶上，就是感情爆发的时候</font></font></font>

981
00:59:12,042 --> 00:59:13,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当时我不顾一切的摸你</font></font></font>

982
00:59:13,708 --> 00:59:15,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你也不顾一切的摸我</font></font></font>

983
00:59:15,458 --> 00:59:17,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还立下永不分离誓言</font></font></font>

984
00:59:21,125 --> 00:59:22,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可惜快乐永远都是短暂的</font></font></font>

985
00:59:22,958 --> 00:59:25,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">换来的只是无穷无尽的痛苦和长叹！</font></font></font>

986
00:59:26,417 --> 00:59:27,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么你会死的？</font></font></font>

987
00:59:28,458 --> 00:59:30,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我当时只有利用月光宝盒使时光倒流</font></font></font>

988
00:59:30,917 --> 00:59:31,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">查出真相</font></font></font>

989
00:59:32,083 --> 00:59:34,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">终于被我发现原来你是自杀的</font></font></font>

990
00:59:35,583 --> 00:59:36,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在最后关头</font></font></font>

991
00:59:37,667 --> 00:59:39,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我终于能够把你救活！</font></font></font>

992
00:59:41,458 --> 00:59:42,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是在最后一次时光倒流</font></font></font>

993
00:59:42,833 --> 00:59:43,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒发生故障</font></font></font>

994
00:59:43,875 --> 00:59:45,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我超的一声回到五百年前</font></font></font>

995
00:59:48,333 --> 00:59:49,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就这样</font></font></font>

996
00:59:53,125 --> 00:59:54,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在想怎么样？</font></font></font>

997
00:59:55,250 --> 00:59:56,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看到你不用再回去了</font></font></font>

998
00:59:57,292 --> 00:59:58,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们成亲！</font></font></font>

999
01:00:00,583 --> 01:00:02,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我…刚刚睡醒</font></font></font>

1000
01:00:02,750 --> 01:00:05,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">经过外面无所事事</font></font></font>

1001
01:00:05,375 --> 01:00:07,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就顺便进来拜师学艺的</font></font></font>

1002
01:00:07,792 --> 01:00:09,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你突然跟我提到成亲这件事</font></font></font>

1003
01:00:10,500 --> 01:00:12,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我…牙齿还没有刷呢！</font></font></font>

1004
01:00:14,417 --> 01:00:16,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道你心里面一定有怀疑</font></font></font>

1005
01:00:16,208 --> 01:00:17,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果我可以把心掏出来给你看</font></font></font>

1006
01:00:17,750 --> 01:00:18,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就会知道我根本没有骗你</font></font></font>

1007
01:00:20,833 --> 01:00:21,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">很简单呀！</font></font></font>

1008
01:00:25,208 --> 01:00:26,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么那么像…</font></font></font>

1009
01:00:26,458 --> 01:00:27,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">椰子是嘛？</font></font></font>

1010
01:00:27,417 --> 01:00:28,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以前有个女孩子也这么说过</font></font></font>

1011
01:00:28,833 --> 01:00:29,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么椰子啊椰子</font></font></font>

1012
01:00:30,000 --> 01:00:31,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他刚才说的话是不是真的？</font></font></font>

1013
01:00:32,875 --> 01:00:33,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别用想了，照旧</font></font></font>

1014
01:00:33,875 --> 01:00:34,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你搜下面！</font></font></font>

1015
01:00:37,792 --> 01:00:38,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谢你了椰子！</font></font></font>

1016
01:00:41,708 --> 01:00:43,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么请问你，他最喜欢的是不是我呀？</font></font></font>

1017
01:00:47,125 --> 01:00:48,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哼！你回来这么久</font></font></font>

1018
01:00:48,958 --> 01:00:51,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一天到晚跟我要月光宝盒</font></font></font>

1019
01:00:51,167 --> 01:00:52,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么意思啊？</font></font></font>

1020
01:00:52,250 --> 01:00:53,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我问你哪天跟我成亲</font></font></font>

1021
01:00:53,792 --> 01:00:55,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你却一直推三推四</font></font></font>

1022
01:00:55,292 --> 01:00:56,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你到底嫁不嫁给我？</font></font></font>

1023
01:00:56,917 --> 01:00:58,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">I do！</font></font></font>

1024
01:01:04,042 --> 01:01:04,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你妹妹是不是疯了？</font></font></font>

1025
01:01:05,042 --> 01:01:06,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个晚上讲鬼话</font></font></font>

1026
01:01:06,833 --> 01:01:08,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她不是疯了，她是神经病</font></font></font>

1027
01:01:09,500 --> 01:01:11,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神经病也行，只要她答应</font></font></font>

1028
01:01:11,208 --> 01:01:12,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">七天后成亲</font></font></font>

1029
01:01:13,958 --> 01:01:15,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你真的决定嫁给他了？</font></font></font>

1030
01:01:16,125 --> 01:01:17,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我骗他的</font></font></font>

1031
01:01:17,375 --> 01:01:18,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我等我的男人回来接我</font></font></font>

1032
01:01:20,958 --> 01:01:23,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你居然会相信那个小猾头会回来接你</font></font></font>

1033
01:01:23,542 --> 01:01:24,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要是真的话，我可得恭喜你啦！</font></font></font>

1034
01:01:25,250 --> 01:01:26,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过就算他回来</font></font></font>

1035
01:01:27,375 --> 01:01:28,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他有什么本事</font></font></font>

1036
01:01:28,417 --> 01:01:29,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把你从牛魔王手上抢回去？</font></font></font>

1037
01:01:30,500 --> 01:01:33,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上天既然安排他能拔出我的紫青宝剑</font></font></font>

1038
01:01:34,417 --> 01:01:36,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他一定是一个不平凡的人</font></font></font>

1039
01:01:37,500 --> 01:01:38,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">错不了</font></font></font>

1040
01:01:38,958 --> 01:01:40,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道有一天</font></font></font>

1041
01:01:40,167 --> 01:01:42,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他在一个万众瞩目的情形下出现</font></font></font>

1042
01:01:43,042 --> 01:01:44,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">身披金甲圣衣</font></font></font>

1043
01:01:44,708 --> 01:01:46,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">脚踏七色云彩来娶我</font></font></font>

1044
01:01:48,417 --> 01:01:49,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还说不是神经病</font></font></font>

1045
01:01:50,708 --> 01:01:53,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这不是神经病！是理想</font></font></font>

1046
01:01:55,917 --> 01:01:56,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">承认吧！小疯子</font></font></font>

1047
01:01:57,042 --> 01:01:57,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不承认！</font></font></font>

1048
01:02:17,333 --> 01:02:19,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">兄弟，世事难料</font></font></font>

1049
01:02:19,667 --> 01:02:21,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没想到你这么快跟白姑娘成亲</font></font></font>

1050
01:02:21,458 --> 01:02:22,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是呀，我自己也没想到</font></font></font>

1051
01:02:22,833 --> 01:02:24,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们都为你高兴！</font></font></font>

1052
01:02:25,333 --> 01:02:26,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谢谢你</font></font></font>

1053
01:02:29,167 --> 01:02:30,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">昨晚你做梦</font></font></font>

1054
01:02:30,250 --> 01:02:32,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">又叫了紫霞姑娘的名字七百八十五次</font></font></font>

1055
01:02:32,833 --> 01:02:34,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">比上次多了一次</font></font></font>

1056
01:02:58,292 --> 01:03:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">过了六天了，明天晚上你就出嫁了</font></font></font>

1057
01:03:03,000 --> 01:03:05,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哼！他会来？才怪</font></font></font>

1058
01:03:27,792 --> 01:03:29,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">昨天晚上我托一只蜘蛛跟你说</font></font></font>

1059
01:03:29,833 --> 01:03:31,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叫牠告诉你，我很想念你</font></font></font>

1060
01:03:32,250 --> 01:03:33,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道呀？</font></font></font>

1061
01:03:35,042 --> 01:03:36,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又知不知道？</font></font></font>

1062
01:03:37,875 --> 01:03:38,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一直在骗你</font></font></font>

1063
01:03:41,042 --> 01:03:42,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">骗就骗吧！</font></font></font>

1064
01:03:42,417 --> 01:03:43,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就像飞蛾一样</font></font></font>

1065
01:03:43,500 --> 01:03:45,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明知道会受伤还是飞扑到火上</font></font></font>

1066
01:03:49,042 --> 01:03:50,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">飞蛾就那么傻！</font></font></font>

1067
01:03:57,917 --> 01:03:58,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出来吧葡萄</font></font></font>

1068
01:04:01,042 --> 01:04:02,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不是想监视你</font></font></font>

1069
01:04:02,875 --> 01:04:04,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只不过想研究一下</font></font></font>

1070
01:04:04,708 --> 01:04:07,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">人与人之间的一些微妙的感情</font></font></font>

1071
01:04:08,625 --> 01:04:09,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你只是强盗啊，大哥</font></font></font>

1072
01:04:09,958 --> 01:04:11,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别学人家学问</font></font></font>

1073
01:04:11,583 --> 01:04:13,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">强盗也有学问</font></font></font>

1074
01:04:14,042 --> 01:04:15,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">省省吧！睡啦！</font></font></font>

1075
01:04:15,833 --> 01:04:18,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞在你心目中是不是一个惊叹号？</font></font></font>

1076
01:04:18,333 --> 01:04:19,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还是一个句号？</font></font></font>

1077
01:04:20,042 --> 01:04:22,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你脑袋里是不是充满了问号呢？</font></font></font>

1078
01:04:23,250 --> 01:04:25,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">紫霞只不过是一个我认识的人</font></font></font>

1079
01:04:25,125 --> 01:04:26,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我以前说过一个谎话骗她</font></font></font>

1080
01:04:26,458 --> 01:04:28,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在只不过心里面有一点内疚而已</font></font></font>

1081
01:04:29,375 --> 01:04:30,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我越来越讨厌她</font></font></font>

1082
01:04:31,125 --> 01:04:32,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我明天就要结婚了，你想怎么样呀？</font></font></font>

1083
01:04:33,833 --> 01:04:34,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有一天当你发觉</font></font></font>

1084
01:04:34,958 --> 01:04:36,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你爱上一个你讨厌的人</font></font></font>

1085
01:04:36,833 --> 01:04:38,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这段感情才是最要命的</font></font></font>

1086
01:04:39,667 --> 01:04:42,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是我怎么会爱上一个我讨厌的人呢？</font></font></font>

1087
01:04:42,917 --> 01:04:45,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">请你给我个理由好不好？拜托！</font></font></font>

1088
01:04:45,500 --> 01:04:47,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">爱一个人需要理由吗？</font></font></font>

1089
01:04:47,417 --> 01:04:48,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不需要吗？</font></font></font>

1090
01:04:48,500 --> 01:04:49,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">需要吗？</font></font></font>

1091
01:04:49,417 --> 01:04:50,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不需要吗？</font></font></font>

1092
01:04:50,250 --> 01:04:50,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">需要吗？</font></font></font>

1093
01:04:50,875 --> 01:04:51,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不需要吗？</font></font></font>

1094
01:04:51,833 --> 01:04:53,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎…我来跟你研究嘛</font></font></font>

1095
01:04:53,250 --> 01:04:56,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干嘛这么认真呢？需要吗？</font></font></font>

1096
01:05:38,708 --> 01:05:39,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁？</font></font></font>

1097
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:54,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">时辰到</font></font></font>

1098
01:06:12,750 --> 01:06:14,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你有多少兄弟姐妹？</font></font></font>

1099
01:06:14,667 --> 01:06:16,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你父母尚在吗？</font></font></font>

1100
01:06:16,458 --> 01:06:17,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说句话啊</font></font></font>

1101
01:06:18,208 --> 01:06:19,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只是想在临死之前</font></font></font>

1102
01:06:19,708 --> 01:06:21,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">多交一个朋友而已嘛</font></font></font>

1103
01:06:23,417 --> 01:06:25,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">糟了，怎么上去救师父？</font></font></font>

1104
01:06:25,625 --> 01:06:28,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以说做妖就像做人一样</font></font></font>

1105
01:06:29,292 --> 01:06:30,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要有仁慈的心</font></font></font>

1106
01:06:31,250 --> 01:06:32,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有了仁慈的心</font></font></font>

1107
01:06:32,792 --> 01:06:35,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就不再是妖，是人妖</font></font></font>

1108
01:06:37,500 --> 01:06:38,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他明白了</font></font></font>

1109
01:06:38,958 --> 01:06:40,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你明白了没有？</font></font></font>

1110
01:06:44,042 --> 01:06:46,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有人会来接你的</font></font></font>

1111
01:06:54,875 --> 01:06:56,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的信</font></font></font>

1112
01:07:03,792 --> 01:07:05,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的良心告诉我</font></font></font>

1113
01:07:05,667 --> 01:07:07,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你最爱的不是我</font></font></font>

1114
01:07:07,833 --> 01:07:08,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">而是另外一个女人</font></font></font>

1115
01:07:09,958 --> 01:07:13,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当我见到她在你良心留下的东西之后</font></font></font>

1116
01:07:13,833 --> 01:07:16,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我觉得，你经过五百年</font></font></font>

1117
01:07:16,458 --> 01:07:19,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">回来要找的不是我，而是她</font></font></font>

1118
01:07:20,875 --> 01:07:23,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你我都要相信这是天意</font></font></font>

1119
01:07:24,375 --> 01:07:26,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也传说中的缘份</font></font></font>

1120
01:07:32,667 --> 01:07:33,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶走了</font></font></font>

1121
01:07:33,583 --> 01:07:34,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道</font></font></font>

1122
01:07:34,333 --> 01:07:35,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">信我看过了</font></font></font>

1123
01:07:35,958 --> 01:07:36,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提大哥</font></font></font>

1124
01:07:36,958 --> 01:07:37,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她怎么啦？</font></font></font>

1125
01:07:41,833 --> 01:07:42,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们看过这封信了吗？</font></font></font>

1126
01:07:42,833 --> 01:07:43,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有呀！</font></font></font>

1127
01:07:43,958 --> 01:07:44,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们看啊</font></font></font>

1128
01:07:45,583 --> 01:07:46,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好</font></font></font>

1129
01:07:47,542 --> 01:07:48,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想走？</font></font></font>

1130
01:07:57,667 --> 01:07:59,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道我师妹白晶晶来过这里</font></font></font>

1131
