1510
01:33:18,875 --> 01:33:19,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你让我走吧！</font></font></font>

1511
01:33:20,875 --> 01:33:22,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好，我让你走</font></font></font>

1512
01:33:23,417 --> 01:33:24,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过临走前你要亲我一下</font></font></font>

1513
01:33:25,458 --> 01:33:26,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">亲一下…</font></font></font>

1514
01:33:26,917 --> 01:33:28,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">亲啊…</font></font></font>

1515
01:33:28,458 --> 01:33:30,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我再怎么说也是个夕阳武士</font></font></font>

1516
01:33:30,792 --> 01:33:31,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你叫我亲我就亲</font></font></font>

1517
01:33:32,458 --> 01:33:33,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那我的形像不是全毁了</font></font></font>

1518
01:33:34,542 --> 01:33:35,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说谎</font></font></font>

1519
01:33:37,042 --> 01:33:38,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不敢亲我</font></font></font>

1520
01:33:38,083 --> 01:33:38,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为你还喜欢我</font></font></font>

1521
01:33:39,542 --> 01:33:40,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我告诉你</font></font></font>

1522
01:33:40,833 --> 01:33:41,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果你这一次拒绝我的话</font></font></font>

1523
01:33:42,042 --> 01:33:43,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你会后悔一辈子</font></font></font>

1524
01:33:44,542 --> 01:33:45,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">后悔我也不会亲</font></font></font>

1525
01:33:46,625 --> 01:33:49,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只能怪相逢恨晚，造物弄人啊</font></font></font>

1526
01:35:32,000 --> 01:35:33,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我这辈子都不会走</font></font></font>

1527
01:35:33,875 --> 01:35:34,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我爱你</font></font></font>

1528
01:35:53,000 --> 01:35:54,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">早就应该这样了！</font></font></font>

1529
01:36:21,500 --> 01:36:22,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干什么？</font></font></font>

1530
01:36:22,708 --> 01:36:24,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那个人的样子好怪啊</font></font></font>

1531
01:36:25,000 --> 01:36:25,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也看到</font></font></font>

1532
01:36:28,417 --> 01:36:29,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他好像条狗啊！</font></font></font>

